ActJudges Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Regulations Made Under the Judges Act
PrecisRegulations Amending Certain Regulations Made Under the JUDGES ACT in order to ensure consistency in the terminology used in the JUDGES ACT and the regulations that are made under it, which will allow for the implementation of the change to the mechanism for the payment of most annuities under the Act.
